"title": "5787: ambition, positive aspects of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5787: ambition, positive aspects of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>In its positive sense, ambition is a personal desire for spiritual progress or achievement.</p>\n<h2>A longing for God and for what he can do in the believer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:6\">MAT 5:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:13-Phil3:14\">PHP 3:13–3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:8\">PSA 40:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:24\">LUK 13:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:29\">COL 1:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:11\">1TH 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:15\">2TI 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1\">HEB 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:2\">1PE 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:14\">2PE 3:14</a></p>\n<h2>The desire for spiritual gifts</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:12\">1CO 14:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:10-1Kgs3:14\">1KI 3:10–3:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:11-2Chr1:12\">2CH 1:11–1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:31\">1CO 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:1\">1CO 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:39\">1CO 14:39</a></p>\n<h2>The desire for a leadership role in the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:1\">1TI 3:1</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The longing for communion with God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:4\">PSA 27:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:25\">PSA 73:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:2\">PSA 84:2</a></p>\n<h2>The compelling desire to preach the gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:20\">ROM 15:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:16\">1CO 9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:15-Phil1:18\">PHP 1:15–1:18</a> <em>Jesus Christ can be proclaimed, despite selfish personal ambition.</em></p>\n<h2>Focus on future rewards</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:24-1Cor9:27\">1CO 9:24–9:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:8\">2TI 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:35-Heb10:36\">HEB 10:35–10:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:26\">HEB 11:26</a></p>",
